reviews.text: Very yummy Indian / Nepalese food and friendly staff. Even better than Anapurna in Tasmania! Can only recommend this place.
Excellent Indian for a good price. nice and spacious restaurant and good service. Came here two times!

The food was extremely underwhelming and the customer service even more. We tried to tell them that the food wasn't up to the mark today but they instead said it was our fault we didn't like it. Would not recommend.

If your taste buds are craving for Indian and Nepali food and you're put up in or nesr Sheung Wan, I highly recommend this place. Consistency and hygienic. Fast and polite service.  This is also a good place for a quick meal on a working day.
Good place for Indian food in HongKong run by Naplese family but make you feel home with their talk and food .

result.name: Namaste kitchen

reviews.text:
在西營盤的最後一晚，來到了這家餐館，異國料理在香港是什麼感覺？踏入裡頭，滿滿的「在地人」，腦袋想到的是：哇，我的英文⋯，，然後是很好，來對地方！
店家很親切，食物很美味，份量、價錢也很實在：
Plain naan:烤餅，柔嫩紮實，份量大
Gurkha chicken curry:雞肉咖喱，肉大塊，另有羊肉可選，味道濃郁
VEG samosas:雜菜咖喱角：一種蔬菜混合的食物，燙喔
Namaste tikki:雜菜薯餅：除了燙，絕對跟妳想的不一樣，綿密的口感然以形容
Mushroom soup 蘑菇湯：除了奶油，該怎麼形容這道湯品呢🤔
Nasi goring :印尼炒飯：油亮的香料炒飯、像瑤柱但顏色不同，裡頭的雞肉是香料雞，上頭一顆太陽蛋，份量紮實啊
Lassi ：印度奶昔，有芒果跟草莓可選，但店家推薦這道local的飲料，為芒果，味道濃郁香氣柔和啊
還有前菜，一道簡單的烤餅，它是放到盤子弄碎，然後沾醬吃，三種特別的味道都可以試試，其中咖喱角的醬也很特別！
非常推薦大家來這品嚐，下次有機會，我也希望在安排時間再過來一次回味！
他的咖喱很地道, 一家幾口營運, 殊不簡單, 值得支持
Very yummy Indian / Nepalese food and friendly staff. Even better than Anapurna in Tasmania! Can only recommend this place.
印度尼泊爾地道美食，味道一流。

是一間以南亞風味為主的餐廳
短期內會再去品嚐
